inn1.comm: starts good length, angles it in just outside off, it straightens, and is played out softly
beaten second ball, Charles comes forward and looks to thump it away from the body through covers, but is beaten by the away swing and bounce
outside edge flies to Rohit Sharma at third slip, but falls inches short, Charles had to play at this one, full on off and middle, and swerving away sharply to take the edge
beaten yet again, with a gentle outswinger
this time he gets bat to ball, the connection is good even as it straightens, and it disappears between extra cover and mid off
Kohli's saved a certain four with a big dive to his right at point, it was shortish and wide, Charles cut hard, Kohli managed to parry it away on the bounce
right on middle stump, pitched up, played out to the off side
straightish line again from Mohit, no movement, and it is picked off the pad in front of square leg
sprays it short and wide outside off stump, though there is some late away movement, it is a wasted delivery
gets it on a good length outside off, no movement again from this line, it is nudged tentatively to midwicket
beats the outside edge now, slants it across close to off stump and gets it to lift past the prod
beaten once more, similar line, similar lift, similar prod, same result
not much swing on this good length ball, it starts too far outside off and is left alone
the inswinger now, he bowls it as a surprise ball early, charles sees the width and attacks it, gets a thick inside edge to pad
length ball holding the line outside off, pushed to point
overpitched and Charles attacks it, scything it down to third man on the bounce, was in the air for a long time but fell well short of the fielder
pitched up to the stumps and straightens into the left-hander late, Powell does well to adjust and clips it past square leg
throws his bat at a widish pitched-up delivery, but underedges it, couple of bounces to the keeper
ending on off stump from a good length, punched down to mid on from the crease
much fuller now, Powell does not get too forward, and drives it to mid off
middle and leg line now, and easily flicked to the right of fine leg, Mohit hasn't generated much movement so far
outside edge now as Powell pushes close to off stump, it hits the bat high but falls several inches short of Ashwin at first slip, hits his wrists and scurries behind
no one at midwicket, Charles jabs a sharp length ball on off in that region and zips across even as Jadeja runs up from mid on
he saw it widish outside off and went for the big drive, but it moved in late and he mistimed it to extra cover
this one straightens now after being angled in closer to off, Charles moves forward and eases it back to the bowler
eased a good length ball outside off stump to extra cover, decent bounce
wider length ball now, and Charles goes after it, flaying it high over extra cover and mid off

here comes the surprise inswinger and Charles has his leg stump uprooted, Charles was probably expecting it to straighten outside off, but it came back a long way with the angle from good length, Charles ended up driving weakly way outside the line
Samuels moves across in the crease, this is another inswinger, bounces from a length and hits him high on the pad
tight line close to off stump, defended to point
overpitched delivery pushed to cover
closes the face of the bat and pushes this full one around off, back to the bowler
overpitched once more, and Powell middles the drive, but he hits it to widish mid off
and for the first time. Mohit manages appreciable movement, but it is off the seam, Mohit's strength, he angles it in, draws Powell forward and beats the outside edge as the ball holds its line
he overpitches it now, and Powell puts it away crisply through cover-point, holds the followthrough on a knee as he watches the ball speed away
defends a length ball to the off side

squared up as he shuffles across in the crease, this straightened from good length, Samuels plays it softly, there is a big gap between the second and third slips, in a late reaction Rohit Sharma tries to stop it with his left hand, but it bursts through
beaten now as another one straightens, this also bounces in front of Dhoni

this comes back in a mile, this is terrific bowling from Bhuvneshwar, starts moving in from far outside off, Samuels had already shouldered arms, it flicks the pad above the knee roll just outside off on its way to the keeper
inswinger again, but ending too far outside off and easily left
now this one holds its line, Samuels is walking across with lots of uncertainty, sees it straighten and lets it go awkwardly
140.8 kph right away, generates plenty of bounce from a good length as Powell prods close to off and is beaten
slants it wider and fuller outside off, Powell swings hard at an attempted square drive, beaten again
gets bat to ball now and punches a length delivery to point
he walks out now, Shami bangs it shortish, Powell has some room and flays it over cover for four more
kicks from back of a length outside off, Powell has a prod again and is beaten
good length on middle now, tucked to midwicket
Samuels walks a long way across outside off and leaves this straightening delivery tentatively
overpitched and squeezed down to third man along the ground even as it holds the line
a late decision to go for the single after a push in front of extra cover but they are home quite safely in the end
bowls it full on off now, Samuels is behind the line to play it out softly
short now, at 135.1 kph, a surprised Samuels reacts alright in the end, dropping the wrists as it kicks at him
short again, and Samuels pulls hard from around off stump, Rohit at squarish midwicket dives to his left and gets a hand to it, a chance, a very improbable one
length ball defended softly
nudges this rising length ball to the leg side, and the single is on even as the bowler runs up to field
pitched up to the pad, flicked down to fine leg
hits a good length at 140.5 kph, bounces and leaves the right-hander widish outside off, and he lets it go
plays a pitched up delivery on off from the crease, gets the bat down in time
punches a 145 kph length ball on the up off the back foot, straight to point
comes forward and runs a 132 kph length ball angled across him, to backward point
the line right on off stump now, fuller too, Powell huriedly jabs it in front of mid on for a quick run
beaten, this was only 130.6 kph but moved in off the seam from good length, Samuels was pushing away from the body and survived
comes in sharply with the angle, into the pad, jabbed square on the leg side
squeezes this length delivery with an open face between cover and point, in the air for a while before it runs into the boundary despite a chase and a slide from Kohli
beaten now with a length delivery angled across the left-hander, how many times has Powell survived this way today
Samuels looks to attack this pitched up delivery, but he is in a pretty poor position, flailing from the crease, and an inside edge rolls to short midwicket
there was plenty of width on this back of a length ball, Samuels went for the punch, but mistimed it and will get only one wide of extra cover
Shami gets the line wrong for the left-hander, sharp length delivery but on the pad, and Powell tucks it superbly through square leg
better line around off stump now, punched from the crease to extra cover
just around off stump again, good length, Powell closes the face as he stabs it back to the bowler
pushes at an overpitched one, and it scurries to square third man
short of a length, he tries nudging to leg, but misses
opens the face and runs this length delivery softly to point
walks out and chases this widish length ball, beaten yet again
pushes a length delivery softly to mid off
moves it across the left-hander from a good length, Powell is playing softly more often that not, and steers it to third man

needless from the bowler, Samuels went for the single after pushing this one close to the pitch on the off side, Bhuvneshwar ran to the ball, picked it up, turned around  and ripped it to the non-striker's end, there was no chance of a run out, and the throw misses the batsman by a couple of feet and the wickets by several, and also runs into the boundary
edgy from Samuels now, he stabs hard at a pitched up delivery and  thick edge flies past the couple of slips
pushes at this one angled across, it runs to third man along the ground
Samuels beaten again as he prods from the crease outside off stump
good length ball, played out off the back foot to point
overpitched on the stumps, Samuels is still not getting forward, but times this superbly, flicking it down the ground through vacant mid on
Powell gets four down the ground now, again not too much of a forward stride, but a flowing, firm followthrough times the ball past mid off
stays in the crease to a back of a length ball and guides it behind point
nice delivery, rising just outside off stump, Samuels drops the wrists late as he stands in the crease
this comes in now to off stump, good length, Samuels, standing in the crease all the time, keeps it out tentatively
short ball now, couple of feet outside off, Samuels reacts well, dropping the wrists and letting it go
ends the over by beating Samuels with a length ball that moves away slightly, Samuels, caught on the crease, uncertainly prods
pushed to sweeper cover for a single
sets himself up for the back-foot punch to this short of a length ball but mistimes it to extra cover
thought about going for the drive, but let this pitched up ball go in the end
opens the face and runs this length delivery to point
dabs a widish length delivery to third man where Shami gets to his left quickly
flows into this drive off a length delivery but finds point

lovely delivery, how many times have the Indians come close to taking a wicket this morning, angled in slightly from Shami, and moves away slightly to beat Samuels, who is found wanting again with his preference for the crease
and again, prods from the crease at another one leaving him and is beaten
gets behind the line this time with a shuffle and defends, he wants to get off strike as he trots out but there is no single here
this one comes in to off stump with the angle, and Samuels squeezes it towards point with an open face
tight line around again, defended from the crease

superb control from Shami this over as he ends with another length ball around off, Samuels jabs it to point, Powell thinks there is a single, he takes half of it before he turns around realising there isn't a run here, he dives but had Yuvraj's throw hit, it would not have saved Powell
Powell walks out now and Mohit bangs it in shortish, it arrives around Powell's ribs, he swivels and gets some bat on the pull to send it fine down the leg side
direct hit now from Bhuvneshwar but Powell was off quickly after driving off the front foot to mid on, and is safely in
Samuels beaten for the umpteenth time here, tries to punch off the back foot but cannot connect
he connects with the punch now, a thick edge sending the ball to third man
drives a pitched up ball straight to mid off
Mohit gets an edge now as he angles it in to the left-hander, but it does not carry to the keeper
tosses it up, Samuels looks to work it to leg, gets a leading edge to the off side
pushed back to the bowler
Samuels has edged and survived, now he steps out early to Ashwin, taking on the flight and sending it way over the long on boundary
and fires it in quick and down the leg side
steps out again but cannot get underneath it enough as he pushes it back
walks out a third time, Samuels is less certain this time and is hit on the pad
takes a boundary off the last ball of the over, Samuels makes room, takes it off the stumps and the back foot punch beats cover, no one sweeping on the off side
gentle offbreak straightens around off and is punched to long off
shortish and very innocuous from Raina, Samuels bashes it through backward point off the back foot
overpitched now and he drives, but to a diving extra cover
drills a full delivery straight to the bowler, Raina fields, then tries to catch the non-striker by surprise by lobbing it back through his legs, it misses the stumps and goes to long on
defended off the front foot
well bowled, this hurried in with the angle to off, Powell brought bat down in time though
stepping out more often than not to Ashwin is Samuels, and earns another run to long on
almost punched it straight back to the bowler, it was in the air but fell just short
tossed up slowly and turns away slightly on off, Powell plays it off the back foot
comes forward and runs a flighted ball behind point
good length offbreak stabbed from the crease to midwicket
he went for the cut, this went on with the angle but Powell was able to time the shot
bit of an appeal as Powell is rapped on the pad but there is a thick inside edge before that
hit to long on for one
played out with the slight spin to midwicket
hurries out but cannot work the ball past midwicket
steered to backward point
length delivery punched down to long on
presses forward to smother a tossed up ball
punched from the crease, extra cover runs to his left, dives and saves one
sharp turn outside off this time, Powell has to reach out to get some bat on it and send it to the sweeper
walks out of the crease, Ashwin shortens it, and Samuels punches to midwicket
wanted to go for the big shot but withdrew late and patted it back
quick, flat, punched to the off side
drives a full one to long off
Samuels looks for the lofted shot down the ground, but does not get hold of it too well, on a couple of bounces to long on
pushed to the bowler
angled in full, Powell cannot get it past the bowler
drags the length shortish, Powell punches it to long on
an appeal for lbw as Raina manages some turn now, but it hit Samuels outside the line of off
goes back to a tossed up ball and pushes to the bowler
pitched up to middle and leg, pushed to midwicket
some turn for Ashwin outside off, Powell slaps it to the sweeper to reach a half-century, he was beaten several times but he's hung on
tossed up ball pushed to midwicket
drives a flighted full delivery to the left of the sweeper
that's right in the gap over extra cover as Powell steps out inside the line and lofts cleanly
punched down to long on
driven to extra cover
fired it into the pad as Samuels came out, but the batsman was able to flick it square
worked off the pad but straight to midwicket
fine stop from the bowler as he throws himself to his right, this was pushed hard by Samuels
length offbreak nudged off the pad behind square leg
stops and delivers it on off stump, nudged to square leg
stop and bowls again, Samuels punches to the sweeper
makes some room and punches to sweeper cover
tossed it up, it went straightish and Samuels pushes it back tentatively
not exactly where he wanted it to go, but Powell's paddled off a top edge from outside off stump straight back over the keeper
punched crisply down to long on
walks out eyeing the leg side but cannot connect and is hit on the pad
second time Powell goes over extra cover and collects four more, skips out and gets inside the line, just beats the fielder's jumps
pushed to sweeper cover
on off and middle, Samuels stabs it straight to midwicket
but Jadeja turns it quite a bit first ball and raps Powell on the pad on the defensive push, but hits him just outside the line of off
swept away to deep square leg
Samuels gets to fifty the way most of his innings has proceeded, scratchily, as he squirts this big lofted shot over cover, it falls in vacant spaces
in control this time as he guides it past point
opens the face and runs it to backward point for a single
Powell sweeps and gets a top edge, but fine leg is up, and it falls short as deep square leg runs to his left
bowled full into middle and leg, clipped to midwicket
and Powell's given it away yet again, off a bigger start this time, nothing delivery really, angled in full some way down the leg side, but it grips, Powell sweeps and top edges to short fine leg
tossed up delivery straightening outside off, played out towards point
left alone outside off stump
sharp turn and some bounce as this goes wide outside off, he reaches out and slaps it to extra cover
full delivery driven past short cover to the sweeper
played out with the spin to midwicket
gets forward and across to nudge it to leg
gets farther across and works it in front of square leg, takes the single after some hesitation
opens the face and waits to see if it beats short third man's dive, it does
moves forward to drive to the sweeper
takes a full ball from outside off and works it to midwicket
that was driven in the air before falling short to Ashwin's left, looked like the straighter one
slapped away to sweeper cover
makes some room and punches, but finds extra cover
comes forward and defends a tossed up ball softly
straightens on off stump, he defends with an open face
lovely, more flight and bite on this one, as it spins and bounces past Bravo's forward push

dropped by Kohli at slip, he puts down catches too often for an otherwise sharp fielder, Samuels was surprised by some extra bounce as he played with an open face, it went straight to Kohli's right off the glove, he dived, got both hands to it and put it down
flicked to short fine leg
comes out and pushes on the off side for a single, there is a misfield which allows a second
goes back and places the cut behind point, the sweeper has some running to do
played out softly on the off side
comes on quickly towards off, is played softly towards point

Ashwin overpitches and Bravo attacks it, he's nowhere close to middling this, he's sliced it high in the air, but the boundaries have been pulled in here, and it eludes Yuvraj's casual one-handed effort at long off, would have had a better chance had he tried to jump and take it
Ashwin drags it short now and Bravo rocks back immediately to pull it hard through midwicket
overpitched ball pushed to long off
turn and bounce outside off, left alone
defended off the front foot
there for the cut but he's chopped it to point
down the track and slams it powerfully past the bowler, it is in the air but quickly past Jadeja's outstretched left hand, Dhawan dives at long on to save the boundary
worked off the pad square on the leg side
comes down the track again, opens the face and takes the single to point
worked with the spin but he finds midwicket now
Ashwin drags it shortish first ball of the Powerplay, it spins down the pad too, and is put away easily to the deep square leg boundary
goes back to a length ball on the stumps and punches

lovely delivery, Ashwin gets one through Samuels' defences, tosses it up, Samuels late in getting forward, the bat hits the front boot as he looks to defend, by then the ball sneaks in through the gate and clips the bails, they decided to see replays to ensure it is not off a rebound from Dhoni
driven to long on for a single
could have been close, he goes back to a flighted ball that hurries on to off stump, Bravo punches just in time
defends a tossed up ball behind point
reaches out to drive to the sweeper
comes forward and stabs a full delivery to backward point
opens the face to one on off stump and runs it to point
good length and spinning away outside off, Simmons chops the cut into the ground
presses well forward to push to extra cover
full and close to off stump, Simmons pushes past Jadeja and goes for the single, bowler takes pace off the shot, extra cover runs in and throws, Simmons was gone if it had been a direct hit
whipped with the spin to deep midwicket
tossed up and angled in, nudged to square leg
superb reflexes from Raina at slip, Bravo underedged the cut and it would have run past Raina on the bounce had he not got his let hand down quickly
Bravo underedges the cut again, this time past the keeper for a couple
nudged behind square leg
leans forward and drives a full delivery from outside off to long on
nice way to end the spell, beaten outside off on the forward push with some turn and bounce
there is no long on, and Simmons slogs this full delivery over mid on, clearing him easily
defended off the front foot
Mohit's sprint and dive from sweeper cover is in vain as the ball rolls into the deep backward point boundary, Simmons timing and placing the cut well
hit on the pad but that was going down leg
presses forward to defend to the off side
Jadeja strikes, Simmons tries another cut but there is some more bounce on this good length ball and he edges it through to Dhoni, not quite the length to cut
starts with a 134.8 kph length ball just outside off, Bravo squeezes it to third man
moves across to defend back to the bowler
back of a length, outside off, Bravo walks across again and blocks
width on a good length, but he cannot time the punch, it rolls to extra cover
bounces him outside off, captain Bravo in control as he drags a pull out to deep midwicket
opens the face to one on middle stump, waits till it beats backward point and takes the single
works a full delivery down to long on
presses forward to block one pitched up to off
into the pad, turned to deep midwicket
some turn into middle stump, punched from the crease to midwicket
worked past Kohli at backward short leg to fine leg
opens the face and drives past extra cover, long off gets to it
a slower one outside off stump, Bravo is already forward and waits to push it to point
punches a length ball down the track well clear of the bowler, but hits the non-striker's stumps
leans across to clip this one angled into middle and leg, out to deep midwicket
another slower one, Bravo holds the forward stride and pushes it wide of point

captain Bravo's holed out to sweeper cover, he went for his favoured extravagant lofted stroke over extra cover, but could not find either timing or placement on this good length delivery, the fielder ran in a few yards from the rope to take a simple catch
steers this length ball on off, but backward point cuts off the single with a dash to his right
comes forward to a tossed up ball and drives it to long off
spins in and hits the pad high as he misses the tuck to square leg
gets bat around front pad to nudge to square leg this time
punched off the back foot for extra cover to make a diving stop
nicely bowled, angled it in at 92 kph on middle and got it to spin past the forward push
Sammy thrusts forward to keep this one out safely
width for the cut, but Jadeja stops a cracking shot at backward point, getting low to his left quickly
opens the face to run a length ball to third man
beaten, 141 kph length ball moves in a shade, past a surprised Sammy's defensive bat, clips the back thigh pad on its way over the stumps to the keeper
squirts this length ball off a thick edge straight to short third man
this is bowled full, Sammy squirts it back down the pitch as he cannot get underneath it, Shami uproots Sammy's middle stump with a sharp throw
hits the gap this time with a punch past extra cover's dive, long off runs around
bat and pad together to defend this to the bowler
tries to swat this behind square off the pad, but misses
there for the cut and Bravo thumps it in front of square
fired into the pad, Bravo heaves, the ball rolls away to deep square leg
he was winding up, Sammy, but decided to defend this back to Jadeja in the end
length delivery swatted in front of square leg
starts just back of a length, Sammy swats a pull but finds deep midwicket
length ball outside leg stump but Bravo cannot take advantage of it as he nudges it behind square leg
full and wide outside off, Sammy reaches for it and drills it wide of the sweeper for a couple
wider still from Bhuvneshwar, Sammy stretches and slams it straight to the sweeper, it bounces awkwardly just in front of the substitute Rayudu, and goes through
cranks up for a big one but chops this length ball into the ground towards point
wide outside off but Sammy cannot beat sweeper cover this time
punched awkwardly and Jadeja sprints to his left to stop it
cannot get under it again as Jadeja fires it into the pad, Sammy works it in front of square leg for a single
bows it wide outside off, Bravo comes across, but gets too close to have a free swing, and drags it weakly to long on
takes a couple behind square leg
Sammy gets under this pitched up delivery but cannot quite find the power, long on hauls it in to his right
gets forward to defend to the bowler
Bravo gets maximum first ball of the over, a good length ball on off and middle, Bravo plonks front foot outside leg and swings this high over long on
appeal for caught behind but umpire Chaudhary is unmoved, faint sound as the full delivery passes Bravo's attempted drive outside off, the bat also hit the ground, difficult to tell
drills a full delivery out to the sweeper
Sammy's swinging and connecting big time on this length ball, clears front leg and mows it straight into the sightscreen
well bowled, gets it up and full in the crease, Sammy cannot get under this, and jams it into the pad
and again, Shami hurls another one into the blockhole on the stumps, and Sammy can only dig it out, Shami's prevented a bad over from turning worse with these two yorkers
starts with a slow back-of-the-hand length ball on off stump, Sammy cranks up and sends it into the gap at deep midwicket
full ball hit down the ground, Rohit concedes an extra run at long on, the ball jamming into his foot, the extra moment allowing Sammy to keep strike
gets it full outside off, Sammy uncoils and throws everything at it, but only gets a thick inside edge behind square leg
goes full and wide, but too wide, just past the marker
pitched up, but some room to swing and Bravo scythes it between extra cover and mid off
he'll get away with a high full toss as Bravo mistimes a heave to extra cover

low full toss drilled down the ground and well stopped at long on, Rohit sprints to his left and throws himself in the path of the ball, parrying it parallel and close to the rope into the hands of long off
a low full toss on off stump, Bravo attacks it, and it flies in the gap through midwicket, too far from long on
cannot get under this full delivery, squeezes it to extra cover on the edge of the circle
Sammy heaves a low full toss from off stump, but he's found deep midwicket, missed out there
there was width on this one angled across, and Bravo powered the drive, but extra cover was in the way
swings hard at a pitched up ball but can only hit it along the ground to long off

Shami ends with another one around the blockhole outside off stump, Bravo guides it past point, he has two by the time the sweeper gets the throw back in, and also reaches his fifty right at the end of the innings, struggled to get going for a while, but he's ended on 51 off 53

inn2.comm: bangs it in shortish, wide and moves it further away
gets it on a better line outside off, swings it away late, left alone
pushes forward with an angled bat expecting away swing, is hit on the inside edge
beaten as he is lured into a loose drive half-forward by an outswinger
in control of this pitched up ball now as he pushes firmly wide of extra cover for a single
opens the face as he comes forward to a 134 kph length delivery, pushes it to point
bowled full and swings in late on off stump, Dhawan pushes solidly to mid off
starts accurate on a good length on off stump, gets good bounce, Rohit pushes softly on the off side and takes an easy single
poor line to the lefthander now, pitched up to his pads, and Dhawan's flick beats fine leg, who is not really very fine
middle and leg now from a good length, played out to midwicket
Holder's still got his line wrong to the left-hander, some inswing taking it fullish on leg, Dhawan now tucks it to the right of fine leg
he corrects the line by angling it outside off, but gives plenty of width and also overpitches it, Dhawan takes a step forward to crash it through the covers
played out to midwicket
short of length ball outside off, Rohit happy to allow it through to the keeper
and again, well away from the stumps, Rohit leaves it alone
short of a length ball closer to off, pushed off the front foot towards cover
fuller and close to off, defended towards point for a quick single
angling across, 135.8kph, Dhawan shoulders arms

boundary to finish the over, just a bit short outside off, Dhawan waits on the back foot and cuts that behind point for four, the fielder in the deep was sprinting to his left to try cut it off but he had no chance as the ball gallops to the boundary
outside off, Rohit is happy to take his time early on, confident that he can up the scoring later, he lets this one go
and another leave outside off
short of a length and outside off, Rohit guides that down to third man for a single, a preferred mode of scoring early on for him
gives Dhawan width, he reaches out and carves that past point for four more, Dhawan racing along here, 20 off 10 with five boundaries
make that 24 off 11, overpitched and closer to off, that is driven past cover for four more, big confident stride forward before unleashing the shot, six boundaries now for Dhawan
shorter and on legstump, defended behind square leg
another leave from Rohit, not too much wrong with the delivery from Rampaul, keeps it tight just outside off

a wicket for West Indies, they needed one early, Rohit fishes at this one just outside off, looking to push towards cover off the front foot, a thick outside edge to first slip, that ball didn't move around much but the superb line just outside off pays off for Rampaul
Kohli shoulders arms to his first delivery, just outside off
wider outside off, another leave
on off stump, defended just in front of point, ponder the single but decide there isn't time for it
another leave and that ends a wicket maiden, exactly what West Indies needed after Dhawan began with a burst of boundaries
starts with a length ball on the pad but gets away with it
width on this length delivery and Kohli smashes it past short cover, but there is a sweeper in place on the boundary
on off stump, pushed past short cover and they trot across for a single
pitched up to off stump, he comes forward to knock it back to the bowler
too wide from Bravo, Kohli reaches out and slaps it just out of the reach of backward point, that was in the air
Bravo consistently bowling a widish line, Kohli comes forward, opens the face and runs it behind point
back of a length ball defended to point from the crease
Kohli slashes at a wide away-swinging ball, and slashes it over the couple of slips
tight line just outside off, and tight forward defence from Kohli
bowls it full into off, Kohli uses the angle to clip it, but finds shortish mid on
Kohli stands tall and slaps this short of a length ball, taking care to beat the man at short cover, superb diving effort from sweeper cover saves the boundary
plays back a good length delivery that came in slightly
eases a good length delivery to covers
Bravo provides width with the angle across Dhawan, who thumps it to the sweeper
Kohli's played a few in the air already today, he goes after a good length delivery on the up, and squirts it just past backward point
goes too hard at a wide ball and chops it down to third man
Dhawan comes out and drives hard through extra cover, the sweeper has it covered, at least it seemed so, before it burst through his hands, sloppy from Simmons
just seems a soft push but the length delivery races behind point, and third man has to run quickly to avoid another four
starts the over with a length ball on the pad, and it beats the keeper's dive
Rampaul corrects the line to around off, Dhawan taps it in front of extra cover for one
just short of a length, punched from the crease, wide of the sweeper for two more

Kohli's gone in trying to leave the ball, it was a late decision, he was all set to defend this length delivery when he decided it was rising too much, tried to withdraw the bat but the ball brushed it and popped up to the keeper
